import React from 'react'
import {Container, Row, Column} from 'react-bootstrap'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
       <footer>
           <Container>
               <Row>
                   <col className="text-center py-3">
                        Copyright © Proshop
                   </col>

               </Row>
           </Container>
       </footer>
    )
}

export default Footer
